CatDescriptText: Cutline of image published in Pittsburgh Courier newspaper, August 3, 1946 reads: "One Of The Leading Ladies! - Lovely Jane Snowden, a specialist in formation swimming and one of the outstanding girl swimmers in this section, will have one of the starring roles in big "Water Circus" at Ammon Center pool next Friday night. She will be starred with Terrance Gorman, the leading male character in the gigantic water extravaganza. - Harris Photo."
TitMainTitle: Jan Snowden, wearing one piece bathing suit with floral front and dark back, and light colored bathing cap, posed on ladder of Ammon recreation center swimming pool
